            Your customers won't wait. Our websites are built to load instantly, keeping visitors engaged from the first click.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <span class="text-accent font-serif text-3xl italic">02</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Clear Design</h3>
