            Showcase your brand without distractions. High contrast and clean layouts ensure your message comes first.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <span class="text-accent font-serif text-3xl italic">03</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Easy Management</h3>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Manage your content without technical headaches. You own every pixel of your professional online presence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

