        Quality that speaks for itself.
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <!-- Principles -->
        <div>
          <p class="uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 text-ink text-sm font-medium">Core Benefits</p>
          <ul class="space-y-8">
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono text-lg">01</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-ink">Search Engine Ready</h3>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  Get found on Google easier. Our websites are built with the structure search engines love, helping you rank higher.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono text-lg">02</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-ink">Rock Solid Experience</h3>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  No annoying jumping or shifting as pages load. Give your visitors a smooth, professional experience on any device.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono text-lg">03</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-ink">Universal Compatibility</h3>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  Your website will look perfect on smartphones, tablets, and desktop computers. No broken layouts or hidden content.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Stack -->
        <div>
          <p class="uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 text-ink text-sm font-medium">The Foundation</p>
          <ul class="space-y-8">
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono text-lg">A</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-ink">Modern Performance</h3>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  Built with the latest technology to ensure your site is incredibly fast and responsive for every visitor.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono text-lg">T</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-ink">Beautiful Styles</h3>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  Custom designs that match your brand identity. Stand out from the competition with a unique look.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
